      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why is there no risk to the customer when a bank prints the customer's name on his cheques?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 7.92,
      "endTime": 15.49,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Name",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "名字"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "When anyone opens a current account at a bank, he is lending the bank money,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "endTime": 20.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "repayment of which he may demand at any time either in cash or by drawing a cheque in favour of another person.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.69,
      "endTime": 29.27,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Primarily, the banker-customer relationship is that of debtor and creditor--",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 29.28,
      "endTime": 35.25,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "who is which depending on whether the customer's account is in credit or is overdrawn.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 35.26,
      "endTime": 40.52,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But, in addition to that basically simple concept,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 40.53,
      "endTime": 43.75,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "the bank and its customer owe a large number of obligations to one another.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 43.76,
      "endTime": 49.71,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Number",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "号码，数字"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Many of these obligations can give rise to problems and complications but a bank customer, unlike, say, a buyer of goods,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 49.72,
      "endTime": 58.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "cannot complain that the law is loaded against him.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.87,
      "endTime": 62.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The bank must obey its customer's instructions, and not those of anyone else.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 62.59,
      "endTime": 67.78,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When, for example, a customer first opens an account, he instructs the bank to debit his account only in respect of cheques drawn by himself.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 67.79,
      "endTime": 77.87,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He gives the bank specimens of his signature, and there is a very firm rule",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 77.88,
      "endTime": 82.81,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "that the bank has no right or authority to pay out a customer's money on a cheque",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.82,
      "endTime": 87.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "on which its customer's signature has been forged.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 87.94,
      "endTime": 91.89,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It makes no difference that the forgery may have been a very skillful one:",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 91.9,
      "endTime": 96.47,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the bank must recognize its customer's signature.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 96.48,
      "endTime": 100.23,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "For this reason there is no risk to the customer in the practice, adopted by banks, of printing the customer's name on his cheques.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 100.24,
      "endTime": 108.99,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Name",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "名字"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "If this facilitates forgery, it is the bank which will lose, not the customer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 109,
      "endTime": 114,
      "analysis": {
